{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"stroke-width","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-width","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n<p><code>stroke-width</code>属性指定了当前对象的轮廓的宽度。它的默认值是<strong>1</strong>。如果使用了一个&lt;percentage&gt;，这个值代表当前视口的百分比。如果使用了<strong>0</strong>值，则将不绘制轮廓。</p>\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它可以直接用作 CSS 样式表内部的属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>类别</th>\n      <th>外观属性</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>值</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Content_type#length\">&lt;length&gt;</a> | <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Content_type#percentage\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> | inherit</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>可变性</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>stroke-width</code>属性：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#shape\">形状元素</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#textcontent\">文本内容元素</a> »</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/painting.html#StrokeWidth","title":"Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)"}],"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.stroke-width"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"stroke-width","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"stroke-width","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"stroke-wid